Class ApplianceItem

java.lang.Object
homeappliance.ApplianceItem
public class ApplianceItem extends Object
A ApplianceItem constructor class. Each appliance item is associated with a specific home appliance and includes additional details such as warranty years, brand, and model. This class provides getter and setter methods to access and modify the fields, as well as a custom `toString` method for a readable string.
Version:
5/1/2025
Author:
Amrit Singh
